    ByteSized, Readable, Receiver<Transmittable>, Transmitter<Transmittable>, NamedObject, PackagePathed, ModificationTimestamped, Broadcaster, Listener, Repeater, Transceiver, ResourcePathed, ReadableResource, Resource, Resourceful
    public class InputResource
extends BaseReadableResource
    An InputStream stream wrapper that allows *one-time* reading of an input stream as a ReadableResource. Once the StreamResource has been opened, it cannot be opened a second time. Attempting to do so will result in an IllegalStateException.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
